    "However, for artificial satellites and space communication in less dense atmospheres, such as those on Mars, the low atmospheric attenuation creates opportunities for utilizing the THz band, offering high data rates.Figure 5C shows a simplified coherent receiver approach for THz data signals [37].",
    "This method involves utilizing an envelope detector and digital signal processing (DSP) for phase reconstruction based on the Kramers-Kronig (KK) receiver concept.",
